# CareerMaster AI — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# The server reads these via os.environ — use `export` or a .env loader.

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# GROQ API KEY (FREE — no credit card required)
# Get yours in 30 seconds at: https://console.groq.com
# Steps:
#   1. Go to https://console.groq.com
#   2. Sign up with GitHub, Google, or email (no credit card needed)
#   3. Click "API Keys" in the left sidebar
#   4. Click "Create API Key", give it a name, copy the key
#   5. Paste it below
# Free tier limits (as of 2026):
#   - llama-3.3-70b-versatile: 6,000 tokens/min, 500,000 tokens/day
#   - llama-3.1-8b-instant:   30,000 tokens/min (used as fallback)
#   - ~14,400 requests/day on free tier
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
